Hello,

I am Antonius Pujo from Indonesia, student of Graduate School of Oriental Studies Iwate University, Japan. My research Theme is Comparason Studies about Bushido in Kinsei and Kindai.

Would you like to tell me How many percent Bushi (samurai) in Edo Period and Early Meiji Period ?

I would like apreciate someone who can help me. Thank you.

Sincerely,
